# Git Workflow Rule

## Branch

| Loại | Pattern |
|------|---------|
| Chính | `main`, `dev` |
| Task | `feat/...`, `fix/...`, `docs/...`, `chore/...`, `test/...` |

## Commit message (Conventional Commits)

```
chore: initialize project structure
feat: add accessible layout
feat: implement jobs api
feat: add docker compose setup
fix: improve focus visible state
fix: connect form error with aria-describedby
docs: add WCAG checklist
```

## Không commit

`.env`, secret, token, credential, `node_modules`, `target`, `dist`, file build thừa.

## Checklist trước merge

- [ ] Build FE (`npm run build`)
- [ ] Build BE (`mvn clean package -DskipTests`)
- [ ] `docker compose config` (nếu sửa Docker)
- [ ] Keyboard navigation (nếu sửa UI)
- [ ] Form label/error (nếu sửa form)
- [ ] README/docs (nếu đổi behavior)

## Tag/release đề xuất

`v0.1-setup` → `v0.2-core-ui` → `v0.3-core-api` → `v0.4-integration` → `v1.0-demo`

## Lưu ý

Chỉ tạo commit khi user yêu cầu rõ ràng.
